  "requirementText": "The CFD model shall be considered acceptable for regulatory submission if the computed relative hemolysis index RH does not exceed 1.10 across all evaluated operating conditions, where RH is defined as the ratio of the candidate device NIH to the predicate device NIH measured under matched flow and rotational speed conditions.",
