      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) reported for NIH quantity of interest. GCI < 5% on fine-to-medium refinement ratio.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the FDA centrifugal pump geometry. GCI for NIH at worst-case operating point (6 L/min, 3500 RPM) is 3.8%, satisfying the 5% threshold. Mesh counts: coarse 2.1M, medium 5.4M, fine 12.8M cells."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
