    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory submission decision. Computed RH values across all five operating points are below the stated acceptance threshold of 1.10, confirming the candidate device does not exceed predicate device hemolysis performance by a clinically significant margin.",
